Author: newthhang
Text: Oh yes, sometimes all I need to do is buy the food and then the cravings go away, but then I have the food and I know I have to eat it (some of it), it is really shitty feeling and I've been trying and (I am kinda doing well for now) to fight it. I don't know why it is in my mind 24/7, it is so annoying honestly, I feel fully out of control like damn, shut up brain.
